    • search

      int search(E element)
      Returns the 1-based position where an element is in this queue. If the element appears multiple times, the position closest to the front is returned.
      Parameters:
      element - the element to search for
      Returns:
      the 1-based position from the front of the queue where the element is located, -1 if the element is not found
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if the specified element is null
